<br><b>E<font size="-1">NTRANCE</font> A<font size="-1">NTIPHON</font></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>Cf. Sir 15: 3-4</i><br>	
<font size="-1">Aqua sapientae potavit eos; firmabitur in illis, et non flectetur, exaltabit eos in aeternum, alleluia.</font><br>	
<font size="+2">H</font>e gave them the water of wisdom to drink;<br>	
it will be made strong in them and will not be moved;<br>	
it will raise them up for ever, alleluia.	
	
