<font size="+2">H</font>ear us, almighty God,<br>	
and, as you have bestowed on your family<br>	
the perfect grace of Baptism,<br>	
so prepare their hearts<br>	
for the reward of eternal happiness.<br>	
Through Christ our Lord.<br>	
