<b>P<font size="-1">RAYER OVER THE</font> O<font size="-1">FFERINGS</font></b><br>
<font size="-1">Concede, quaesumus, Domine, semper nos per haec mysteria paschalia gratulari, ut continua nostrae reparationis operatio perpetuae nobis fiat causa laetitiae.</font><br>		
<font size="+2">G</font>rant, we pray, O Lord,<br>	
that we may always find delight in these paschal mysteries,<br>	
so that the renewal constantly at work within us<br>	
may be the cause of our unending joy.<br>	
Through Christ our Lord.<br><br><br>	
