<br><b>E<font size="-1">NTRANCE</font> A<font size="-1">NTIPHON</font></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>Cf. Ps 18 (17): 50; 22 (21): 23</i><br>	
<font size="-1">Confitebor tibi in populis, Domine, et narrabo nomen tuum fratribus meis, alleluia.</font><br>	
<font size="+2">I</font> will praise you, Lord, among the nations;<br>	
I will tell of your name to my kin, alleluia.<br><br>	
<br>	
	
<b>C<font size="-1">OLLECT</font></b><br>	
<font size="-1">Annua recolentes mysteria, quibus per renovatam originis dignitatem humana substantia spem resurrectionis accepit, clementiam tuam, Domine, suppliciter exoramus, ut, quod fide recolimus, perpetua dilectione capiamus.</font><br>
