<font size="+2">O</font> God, who by the wonderful exchange effected in this sacrifice<br>	
have made us partakers of the one supreme Godhead,<br>	
grant, we pray,<br>	
that, as we have come to know your truth,<br>	
we may make it ours by a worthy way of life.<br>	
Through Christ our Lord.<br><br><br>	
