<font size="-1">Dicit Dominus: Ego elegi vos de mundo et posui vos ut eatis, et fructum afferatis, et fructus vester maneat, alleluia.</font><br>	
<font size="+2">I</font> have chosen you from the world, says the Lord,<br>	
and have appointed you to go and bear fruit,<br>	
