<br>	
<br><b>E<font size="-1">NTRANCE</font> A<font size="-1">NTIPHON</font></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>Cf. Ps 68 (67): 8-9, 20</i><br>	
<font size="-1">Deus, dum egredereris coram populo tuo, iter faciens eis, habitans in illis, terra mota est, caeli distillaverunt, alleluia.</font><br>	
<font size="+2">O</font> God, when you went forth before your people,<br>	
marching with them and living among them,<br>	
the earth trembled, heavens poured down rain, alleluia.<br><br>	
<br>	
	
<b>C<font size="-1">OLLECT</font></b><br>	
<font size="-1">Deus, qui pro salute mundi sacrificium paschale effecisti, propitiare supplicationibus populi tui, ut interpellans pro nobis Christus Pontifex noster, nos per id quod nostri est similis reconciliet, per id quod tibi est aequalis absolvat.</font><br>
