who called you out of darkness into his wonderful light, alleluia.<br><br>	
<br>	
	
<b>C<font size="-1">OLLECT</font></b><br>	
<font size="-1">Depelle, Domine, conscriptum peccati lege chirographum, quod in nobis paschali mysterio per resurrectionem Christi Filii tui vacuasti.
