<br><b>C<font size="-1">OMMUNION</font> A<font size="-1">NTIPHON</font></b>	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>	
<font size="-1">Surrexit Pastor bonus, qui animam suam posuit pro ovibus suis, et pro grege suo mori dignatus est; alleluia.</font><br>	
<font size="+2">T</font>he Good Shepherd has risen,<br>	
who laid down his life for his sheep<br>	
