<br>	
<br>	
<b>P<font size="-1">RAYER AFTER</font> C<font size="-1">OMMUNION</font></b><br>
<font size="-1">Gregem tuum, Pastor bone, placatus intende, et oves, quas pretioso Filii tui sanguine redemisti, in aeternis pascuis collocare digneris.	</font><br>	
