Who lives and reigns for ever and ever.<br>	
<br>	
<br>	
<b>S<font size="-1">OLEMN</font> B<font size="-1">LESSING</font></b><br>	
<font size="+2">M</font>ay God, who by the Resurrection of his Only Begotten Son<br>	
