<b>C<font size="-1">OLLECT</font></b><br>	
<font size="-1">Deus, qui humanam naturam supra primae originis reparas dignitatem, respice ad pietatis tuae ineffabile sacramentum, ut, quos regenerationis mysterio dignatus es innovare, in his dona tuae perpetuae gratiae benedictionisque conserves.</font><br>
<font size="+2">O</font> God, who restore human nature<br>	
to yet greater dignity than at its beginnings,<br>	
look upon the amazing mystery of your loving kindness,<br>	
and in those you have chosen to make new<br>	
through the wonder of rebirth<br>	
may you preserve the gifts<br>	
of your enduring grace and blessing.<br>	
Through our Lord Jesus Christ, your Son,<br>	
who lives and reigns with you in the unity of the Holy Spirit,<br>	
God, for ever and ever<br>	
<br>	
