<font size="+2">M</font>ay our prayers rise up to you, O Lord,<br>	
together with the sacrificial offerings,<br>	
so that, purified by your graciousness,<br>	
we may be conformed to the mysteries of your mighty love.<br>	
Through Christ our Lord.<br><br><br>	
