<br><b>C<font size="-1">OMMUNION</font> A<font size="-1">NTIPHON</font></b>	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  <i>Mt 28: 20</i><br>	
<font size="-1">Ecce ego vobiscum sum omnibus diebus, usque ad consummationem saeculi, alleluia.</font><br>	
<font size="+2">B</font>ehold, I am with you always,<br>	
even to the end of the age, alleluia.<br>	
<br>	
<br>	
<b>P<font size="-1">RAYER AFTER</font> C<font size="-1">OMMUNION</font></b><br>
<font size="-1"> Omnipotens sempiterne Deus, qui ad aeternam vitam in Christi resurrectione nos reparas, fructus in nobis paschalis multiplica sacramenti, et fortitudinem cibi salutaris nostris infunde pectoribus.</font><br>	
<font size="+2">A</font>lmighty ever-living God,<br>	
who restore us to eternal life<br>	
in the Resurrection of Christ,<br>	
increase in us, we pray, the fruits of this paschal Sacrament<br>	
and pour into our hearts the strength of this saving food.<br>	
Through Christ our Lord.<br><br>	
